data.description: This beautiful partially remodeled 4 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom Cape Cod style brick house is a gem. With 1225 square feet of space, it offers a cozy and comfortable living environment. The large corner lot provides plenty of outdoor space for activities and relaxation. The full unfinished basement offers potential for customization and additional living space. The new black gutters add a stylish touch to the exterior. Inside, the corian countertops in the kitchen add a touch of elegance. The two-car garage with dual garage doors ensures ample parking and storage space. It's a dream home! Seller will give a $5,000 credit on behalf of the buyer for closing.
